											>
												<h3 class="mb-2">Users Diversity:</h3>
												<p>
													Here are a brief on the main users of Smart School
													Management System, and the key tasks that can be
													managed by it. The number of system users is
													determined according to the size of the school, its
													activities, employee positions, and number of
													students.
												</p>
												<figure class="figure text-center mt-4">
													<img
														src="../src/assets/images/pdf/pdf1_en.webp"
