											<!-- Key Features -->
											<div
												class="box overflow-hidden"
												data-section="Key Features"
											>
												<h3 class="mb-2">Key Features:</h3>
												<ol>
													<li>
														<p>
															Supports user interfaces compatible with various
															device screens.
														</p>
													</li>
													<li>
														<p>
															Provides educational follow-ups, and performs
															immediate administrative actions, as the system
															integrates the tasks of the different users
															including: administrators, teachers, pedagogical
															supervisors, examination officers, students,
															parents, etc.
														</p>
													</li>
													<li>
														<p>
															Monitors the teachers’ attendance and enables
															viewing the readiness of substitute teachers to
															cover the classes of the absentees.
														</p>
													</li>
													<li>
														<p>
															Accepts linking to remote virtual classroom
															software in order to deliver lessons and
															explanations online.
														</p>
													</li>
													<li>
														<p>
															Links to online payment platforms, such as PayPal,
															2Checkout, and PayMoney.
														</p>
													</li>
													<li>
														<p>
															Supports multiple languages including English,
															Arabic, French, and Turkish, and allows adding new
															languages as required. It also supports both Hijri
															and Gregorian calendars.
														</p>
													</li>
													<li>
														<p>
															Enables the system administrator to get and
															install updates on the school system website.
														</p>
													</li>
													<li>
														<p>
															Allows setting quizzes without scores for
															kindergarten children.
														</p>
													</li>
												</ol>
												<div class="row textimg">
													<div class="col text-center">
														<i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt fa-3x"></i>
														<p>
															Teachers are the most important users of the
															school system, as they record the learning
															progress of their students.
														</p>
													</div>
