														<p>
															Defining the school buildings, departments, and
															divisions.
														</p>
														<p></p>
													</li>
													<li>
														<p>
															Defining teachers including their main data,
															academic qualifications, and contact details.
														</p>
														<p></p>
													</li>
													<li>
														<p>
															Defining the educational stages including the
															classrooms, sections, students, and the supervisor
															of each stage.
														</p>
														<p></p>
													</li>
													<li>
														<p>
															Defining grades and the maximum number of students
															per class.
														</p>
														<p></p>
													</li>
													<li>
														<p>
															Defining administrators, accountants, and
															educators in the school according to their
															responsibilities.
														</p>
														<p></p>
													</li>
													<li>
														<p>
															Coding any additional fields that may be needed by
															the school, such as ID type and number, guardian
															kinship, etc.; and coding files to be uploaded on
															the system.
														</p>
														<p></p>
													</li>
													<li>
														<p>
															Implementing the financial settings of the general
															ledger, such as building a chart of accounts,
															defining expenses, fees, taxes, electronic payment
															platforms, etc.
														</p>
														<p></p>
													</li>
												</ol>
